<translate>
== Usage ==

In a SpreadSheet, delect one or several cells, then run the macro. Choose the information you want to display.

The refresh button image recalculates the analysis, for example after you modify a cell or change the selection. The expand/collapse button lets you expand or collapse the whole tree. You can also do it branch by branch by clicking on the ▶ or ▼ symbols.

